dialog.body: Hello, thank you for contacting Old Stone Auto Insurance. My name is Jack Wright. May I have your name, please?
Nice to meet you, Abigail. Can you please provide me with your policy number?
Yes, it's eight one two zero.
Thank you. Now, could you confirm your date of birth for verification purposes?
Sure, it's zero four dash two five dash one nine eight seven.
Great, thank you for confirming that. Do you have any specific questions regarding your policy coverage or any recent incidents to report?
Not at the moment, just checking on my premium payment schedule.
I can assist you with that. Your next premium payment is due on the fifth of next month. Thank you for reaching out, Abigail. Is there anything else I can help you with today?
No, that's all. Thank you for your help, Jack. Goodbye.
You're welcome, Abigail. Have a great day. Goodbye.
